  <md:title>The Tyranny and Triumph of the Majority</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Explain Alexis de Tocqueville’s analysis of American democracy</item>
<item>Describe the election of 1840 and its outcome</item>
</list></md:abstract>
