<term>log cabin campaign</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm25803520">the 1840 election, in which the Whigs painted William Henry Harrison as a man of the people</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp173832016">
<term>second party system</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm32162688">the system in which the Democratic and Whig Parties were the two main political parties after the decline of the Federalist and Democratic-Republican Parties</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm17153792">
<term>tyranny of the majority</term>
